<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$wonderxhd" href="/people/wonderxhd">向华东</a>，<strong title="留欧脑科学博士；智精灵教育科技CEO；我爱脑科学网/心心水滴论坛创始站长。" class="zu-question-my-bio">留欧脑科学博士；智精灵教育科技CEO；我…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="3">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$njubianyuan" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/njubianyuan" class="zg-link" title="卞远">卞远</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$JackyZhu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/JackyZhu" class="zg-link" title="朱松清">朱松清</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$pirate-henry" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/pirate-henry" class="zg-link" title="Pirate Henry">Pirate Henry</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="185976" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">这个，就是用计算机尽力去模拟人脑的生理功能。  <br> 当前脑科学研究发展神速，然而离揭开思维的奥秘还有待时日。因此能否模拟，不光是计算机超不超级的问题，更是我们对人脑运行规律已知了多少的问题。


</div>

</div>
